who he is or how he got here.

236
00:09:53.567 --> 00:09:56.633
Or what a car is. Yeah.

237
00:09:56.767 --> 00:09:58.800
Okay. well. I'll run him
by the hospital

238
00:09:58.934 --> 00:10:01.467
