and get him checked out.

239
00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:02.500
Thank you.

240
00:10:02.633 --> 00:10:03.767
Oh. hey.

241
00:10:03.900 --> 00:10:05.033
Actually. while I'm here.

242
00:10:05.166 --> 00:10:06.100
